.000Z","msg":"攬炒我啲乜? 真心求教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:13:58.000Z","msg":"你嘅綜援可能唔能夠準時發放"},{"pid":"07486d881d3cf0877f4390f85507d135b01f8c68","tid":2025240,"uid":211466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"717dec38e5ea22c3d2c6eb48aa1b1c35462f612a","tid":2025240,"uid":139322,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"caba77eafac8281c6e02e40e3fa8ca5749a2ba24","tid":2025240,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629dc153e406c4bf050c6676c688b27d06affea1","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"Good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"hi coco哥"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T07:53:46.000Z","msg":"鬼係COCO哥咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:38:34.000Z","msg":"coco 哥有好野會上連登免費益你?<br />\n我唔信喇"},{"pid":"6011acfce0ca31e3a7763343001884f80f028145","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:48:06.000Z","msg":"Coco Gor 投資書已經出版, 各大書店有售, 想學嘢記得快啲買嚟睇! 我誠意推薦.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QHKRPDK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQHKRPDK.jpg&h=278aa116&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發達大計，諗起都開心！<br />\n<br />\n這是個資訊爆炸的年代，也是充斥假消息的年代。面對選擇無窮的年代，如何作最精明選擇？<br />\n<br />\n好多朋友都跟我講，投資、買樓是件令人很頭痛的事，根本不知道從何開始。由於覺得很麻煩，於是便放棄學習理財方法。他們甚至發展出一套理論：認為努力工作賺錢才是正途，經投資所得都是「不義之財」。<br />\n<br />\n在本書中，我會從個人的親身經驗角度出發，教大家如何買股票、買債券、買樓，甚至買外國樓。希望給未有相關經驗的朋友，有所啟發。<br />\n<br />\n「成功的人找方法，失敗的人找說法。」投資其實唔難，大家只要堅持，自然會找出方法。希望大家都成功。"},{"pid":"284787f471a18dea5667c359778f77b17d4dde63","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"caba77eafac8281c6e02e40e3fa8ca5749a2ba24","tid":2025240,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629dc153e406c4bf050c6676c688b27d06affea1","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"707ed0916363a7c39934606dbe81dd48b0e80414","tid":2025240,"uid":14918,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:26:18.000Z","msg":"對平民無<br />\n對權貴有<br />\n<br />\nIF平民burns, 權貴 burn with us."},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"Good <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:35:23.000Z","msg":"hi coco哥"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"Coco Gor 投資書已經出版, 各大書店有售, 想學嘢記得快啲買嚟睇! 我誠意推薦.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H3fp9Ex.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH3fp9Ex.jpg&h=dbf6227a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fa53655a7a998d92adac2aa825dca4746f9ef85","tid":2025240,"uid":152040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"284787f471a18dea5667c359778f77b17d4dde63","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"caba77eafac8281c6e02e40e3fa8ca5749a2ba24","tid":2025240,"uid":209773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"629dc153e406c4bf050c6676c688b27d06affea1","tid":2025240,"uid":353278,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T06:28:56.000Z","msg":"Good <img src=\"/assets/faces